                <h1>Reed Hastings: Innovator Behind Netflix's Streaming Revolution</h1>
                <p>Reed Hastings, the co-founder and CEO of Netflix, revolutionized the entertainment industry by introducing a subscription-based streaming service. His vision transformed how people consume media, shifting from traditional video rentals to on-demand streaming. Hastings is a notable advocate for educational reform and innovation in technology.</p>
